{"tid":1468061,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請各位手足唔好俾仇恨支配，忘記和你飛行動嘅初衷","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:53:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T02:19:49.000Z","uid":67182,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"460f3120ca67f10d08296963c7a9ec87b415ae40","tid":1468061,"uid":67182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:53:43.000Z","msg":"和你飛行動主要有兩大目的<br />\n<br />\n1. 反映我地嘅訴求，令到國際關注香港，等佢地知道我地係受壓迫嘅一方，從而透過輿論去打擊對家<br />\n<br />\n2. 經濟制裁，停止機場運作，令經濟損失達至千萬計，從而令政府跪低<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日已經好亂，唔想評論究竟勇武定和理非嘅比較好。<br />\n開始呢post只係想提醒返大家，唔好迷失方向，因為係我地面前仲有五大訴求！<br />\n<br />\n希望經過今晚，每一位手足都諗清楚，再改善之後嘅行動。"},{"pid":"2deb5b19fd0b809d4726f72483fab14f5da310e0","tid":1468061,"uid":67182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:55:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8e6e1f31e08f2f66384e2427b808c68f3a3a6a8c","tid":1468061,"uid":67182,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:56:55.000Z","msg":"希望大家睇到"},{"pid":"5a1e8913e5bd2e74084a56a3a246d4692f389af6","tid":1468061,"uid":67182,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:13:37.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"87fd4f401bb80dcdb8b088756b695452faa78617","tid":1468061,"uid":67182,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:18:07.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"80cd9aee23272abafee3ac5bfe70a43475de1341","tid":1468061,"uid":67182,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:18:25.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"e4d620e430e901e77679d206254129744f3d3c04","tid":1468061,"uid":67182,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:21:42.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"becdd1188ffce598a2baa4affb9f0058989d67f1","tid":1468061,"uid":67182,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:02:49.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"71df49c15938404045689c897ab56616d27476e6","tid":1468061,"uid":178933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:15:18.000Z","